What is buffer in c language. ?

   i want to allocate 2*650000 byte of memory in c language to open one
   binary file and extract data of it(data are in 12 bit format so we need
   2 byte to save one data). someone suggest me to use buffers but i don't
   know how and what kind of this buffer must use.
   Follow
   5 answers 5
   Report Abuse
